+# [MonBlog]
+
+source :  this application has been designed based on [Evoluer vers une architecture MVC en PHP] (http://bpesquet.developpez.com/tutoriels/php/evoluer-architecture-mvc/)
+		   footer has been developped based on https://www.script-tutorials.com/stylish-responsive-footer/
+		   design is based on bootstrap (https://getbootstrap.com/getting-started/, http://www.w3schools.com/bootstrap/default.asp)
+Author : [jpguilleron@hotmail.com]
+
+## Version
