+## Description
+
+* MVC architure framework
+* Blog application version 0.1.0
+* Chat application version 0.1.0
+* Login application version 0.1.0
+* Shop application version 0.1.0
+* Todo application version 0.1.0
+* Contact application version 0.0.1

+## Configuration setup
+
+modify dev.ini to cope with the actual configuration - create a prod.ini for production (prod.ini override dev.ini)
+ config file *.ini:
[Configuration]
site.application.version = v2016-13			// VERSION to be updated for each version
site.application.name = netricite			// Application name to be updated for each project
site.application.index = root       		// default page launched 

[Debug]
debug = true						; production change debug to false
debug.trace = true					; production change debug to false
debug.framework = true				; production change debug to false

+## Eclipse project clone
+
+* 1. From explorer nor eclipse DO NOT duplicate project 
+* 2. From eclipse open a new project in the root directory  d:wamp/www/netricite/
+* 3. Import a previous version in the new created project
+* 4. change config setup as describe above

+## New function
+
+* 1. From eclipse create new folders in controler, model, view folders with the name of the function
+* 2. From eclipse create one PHP file per folder with the name of the application in every new folder (cApplication, mApplication, vApplication) based on cGenerator, mGenerator, vGenerator 
+* 3. add new menu item in vMenu
+* 4. if login is required cGenerator extends fw\fwControlerFilter


